thread.title: ‍Eniro Says Q4 ‍Total Operating Revenue Amounted To Sek 374 M, A Decrease Of 22%

author: Reuters Editorial
title: ‍Eniro Says Q4 ‍Total Operating Revenue Amounted To Sek 374 M, A Decrease Of 22%
text:
Feb 13 (Reuters) - Eniro Ab:
* ‍ENIRO‘S YEAR-END REPORT 2017 - TRANSLATION​
* ‍FY TOTAL OPERATING REVENUE AMOUNTED TO SEK 1,595 M (1,967), A DECREASE OF 19%​
* ‍FY EBITDA DECREASED BY 60% TO SEK 173 M​ * FY ‍NET INCOME FOR PERIOD WAS SEK 76 M​ * FY ‍EARNINGS PER ORDINARY SHARE FOR PERIOD WERE SEK 0.05 (-1.88) BEFORE AND AFTER DILUTION​
* Q4 ‍TOTAL OPERATING REVENUE AMOUNTED TO SEK 374 M (479), A DECREASE OF 22%​
* Q4 ‍EARNINGS PER ORDINARY SHARE FOR PERIOD WERE SEK 0.06 (-0.10) BEFORE AND AFTER DILUTION​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
